title: Rainforest Creations
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Western, Take-out only
description: Part of a chain of market stalls specializing in raw foods. Menu includes wraps, salad, and "flan" boxes. Most items priced at either £3 or £5, and the only non-vegan item is a mung bean salad which contains honey.
streetAddress: Chelsea Market, Duke of York Square, Kings Road
